							<ul class="nova-list">
								<li>Licensed & Insured</li>
								<li>Background-Checked Team</li>
								<li>Eco-Friendly Cleaning Options</li>
								<li>Flexible Scheduling (Nights & Weekends Available)</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						<div class="split-content-item">
							<ul class="nova-list">
								<li>Custom Maintenance Plans</li>
								<li>Responsive Communication</li>
								<li>Transparent Pricing</li>
								<li>Satisfaction Guaranteed</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="split-content-item">
					<h1>Ready To Get Started?</h1>
					<p>Whether you need routine janitorial service or specialty cleaning, Nova Facility Solutions is ready to create a customized plan for your property.</p>
					<p>Request a Quote Today or Contact Our Team To Discuss Your Needs</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</div>
